e system metric values captured for the most current time interval for both the long duration (60-second) and short duration (15-second) system metrics.\n显示系统度量值(有各个pool的命中率)，这个值捕获当前时间前推60秒和前推15秒的统计。',3597,'2016-04-08 19:52:08','2016-04-08 19:52:08',2147),(1320,'使用PL/SQL来优化sql text使之统一格式化','PL/SQL执行sql语句会统一把SQL语句改为大写，多余的空格合并为一个空格。\n出自--Oracle Database 10g 性能调整与优化(122页 4.5.1)',3598,'2016-04-08 19:52:08','2016-04-08 19:52:08',2040),(1321,'library cache概念','Library cache 查找sql的计算基于构建词语句的字符的ASCII值，所以SELECT（大写）和select（小写），是不同的语句，需要再次解析。',3598,'2016-04-08 19:52:08','2016-04-08 19:52:08',2047),(1322,'两个不同的sql语句，但是object可以共享解析','select * from orders;和select sum(order_amount) from orders虽然是不同的语句，但是DD cache中，orders这个对象已经缓存在DD中了。',3598,'2016-04-08 19:52:08','2016-04-08 19:52:08',2048),(1323,'存储的PLSQL比匿名PLSQL执行要快','因为存储的plsql是存储数据字典中的，而匿名不是所以，对于再次执行而言，不能被cache 和重用。',3598,'2016-04-08 19:52:08','2016-04-08 19:52:08',2049),(1324,'DD与library cache调优优先级','SGA中分配内存算是首先分配字典缓存，所以，如果library cache正确无误，DD cache也必然正确。',3598,'2016-04-08 19:52:08','2016-04-08 19:52:08',2050),(1325,'dbms_shared_pool.purge','--dbms_shared_pool.purge(\'1EFB91B8, 3642190903\',\'C\');\n--ADDRESS和HASH_VALUE,C是cursor的意思\n--把某条sql语句从shared pool中flush掉',3599,'2016-04-08 19:52:08','2016-04-08 19:52:08',2608),(1326,'清除shared pool中的对象','ALTER SYSTEM FLUSH SHARED_POOL;',3600,'2016-04-08 19:52:08','2016-04-08 19:52:08',2114),(1327,'SHARED_POOL_SIZE','#设置asm sga中 shard pool的大小。',3601,'2016-04-08 19:52:08','2016-04-08 19:52:08',1340),(1328,'CURSOR_SHARING',NULL,3601,'2016-04-08 19:52:08','2016-04-08 19:52:08',2041),(1329,'SHARED_POOL_RESERVED_SIZE','设置保留池的大小',3601,'2016-04-08 19:52:08','2016-04-08 19:52:08',2059),(1330,'cursor_space_for_time','弃用',3601,'2016-04-08 19:52:08','2016-04-08 19:52:08',2084),(1331,'shared pool--查看shared pool命中率','select ((1-(sum(getmisses) / (sum(gets) + sum(getmisses))))*100) hit_rate \nfrom v$rowcache \nwhere gets+getmisses<>0;\n',3602,'2016-04-08 19:52:08','2016-04-08 19:52:08',1551),(1332,'shared pool--查看各个组件的内存大小','SELECT POOL,NAME,BYTES FROM V$SGASTAT WHERE POOL=\'shared pool\';\n',3602,'2016-04-08 19:52:08','2016-04-08 19:52:08',1761),(1333,'data dictionary--查看data dictionary命中率','select ((1-(sum(getmisses)/(sum(gets)+sum(getmisses))))*100) \"Hit Rate\" from v$rowcache where gets+getmisses<>0;\n--命中率应该在95%以上.',3602,'2016-04-08 19:52:08','2016-04-08 19:52:08',2035),(1334,'library cache--查看librarycache的整体reload率','select  sum(pins) \"Hits\",sum(reloads) \"Misses\",((sum(reloads)/sum(pins)) *100) \"Reload %\" from v$librarycache;\n',3602,'2016-04-08 19:52:08','2016-04-08 19:52:08',2043),(1335,'shared pool--查看的当前大小/空余空间/百分比','select S.CURRENT_SIZE/1024/1024 \"Current Shared Pool MB\",g.bytes/1024/1024 as \"Free MB\",g.bytes/s.current_size  \"Percent Free\" from V$SGA_DYNAMIC_COMPONENTS s,v$sgastat g where s.component=\'shared pool\' and g.name=\'free memory\' and g.pool=\'shared pool\';',3602,'2016-04-08 19:52:08','2016-04-08 19:52:08',2044),(1336,'data dictionary--查看数据字典中命中率详单','select parameter,gets,getmisses,modifications,flushes,\n	(getmisses/decode(gets,0,1,gets)) getmiss_ratio,\n	(case when(getmisses/decode(gets,0,1,gets))>0.1 then \'*\'else\' \'end) \" \" \nfrom v$rowcache \nwhere gets+getmisses<>0;\n--当最后一列为*时，说明此行的数据字典区域命中率低于90%',3602,'2016-04-08 19:52:08','2016-04-08 19:52:08',2051),(1337,'library cache--查看命中率','select sum(pins) \"Hits\",sum(reloads) \"Misses\",(sum(pins)/(sum(reloads)+sum(pins))*100) \"HIT RATIO%\" from v$librarycache;',3602,'2016-04-08 19:52:08','2016-04-08 19:52:08',2052),(1338,'library cache--查看各个namespace命中率详单','select namespace,\n    GETHITRATIO*100 GETHITRATIO,--get命中率\n    PINHITRATIO*100 PINHITRATIO,--pin命中率\n    reloads,--reload次数\n    reloads/decode(pins,0,1,pins)*100 reloadratio --reload和pin的比率\nfrom v$librarycache;\n--get命中率和pin名中应该接近1',3602,'2016-04-08 19:52:08','2016-04-08 19:52:08',2053),(1339,'shared pool--查看library cache中每一个chunk的类型','SELECT sum(ksmchsiz) bytes,ksmchcls status FROM X$KSMSP group by ksmchcls;\n-